    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo describes a new RFC 2822 message header, "Message-Context".  This header provides information about the context and presentation characteristics of a message.  A receiving user agent (UA) may use this information as a hint to optimally present the message. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
